## Setting up a Gateway

I set up an S3 Gateway, which is a type of endpoint used specifically for Amazon S3 and DynamoDB .

### What are endpoints?

An endpoint in AWS is a service that allows private connections between your VPC and other AWS services without needing the traffic to go over the internet.

![Image](http://nextwork.ai/soothed_gold_swift_blueberry/uploads/aws-networks-endpoints_09bcaa8a)

